               <occupation type="ecclesiastic">saint</occupation>
       
     
               <floruit> He was a saintly monk of  the spiritual line of <roleName type="title">ʾabbā</roleName> 
                  <persName ref="PRS1955Anorewos">ʾAnorewos “the Elder”</persName> in the 15th century. 
                  He was born from  his father <persName ref="PRS1883Ammehas">ʾAmmǝḫa Ṣǝyon</persName> who was the head of the 
                  royal army and <persName ref="PRS10616ZaraA">Zarʾa ʾAbrǝham</persName> was raised to be a soldier 
                  and assumed his father's position after the later death. However, he left his military role and became a warrior for God.</floruit>
           
